OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779354384
OL,3,CSummerland families begin legal
OL,4,Cchallenge to reopen inquests
OL,6,FThe families of victims and survivors
OL,7,Fof the Summerland fire disaster have
OL,8,Ftaken their fight for a fresh inquest
OL,9,Fto Douglas Courthouse.
OL,11,FFifty people lost their lives in the
OL,12,Ffire at the Summerland leisure centre
OL,13,Fon the Isle of Man on 2 August 1973,
OL,14,Fand campaigners are now calling on the
OL,15,F"death by misadventure" verdict to be
OL,16,Foverturned.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
